cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.SE, cs.SI, cs.HC 

This paper deals with security vulnerabilities in home network routers and their web interfaces. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also discusses network infrastructure (NI) and software engineering (SE) aspects of router security. Additionally, the paper provides countermeasures to improve the user interface (SI) and human-computer interaction (HC) of router administration interfaces.
